      <title>俄罗斯周通胀率 18 个月来首次转为负值</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/russian-weekly-inflation-goes-negative-in-first-for-18-months</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯央行于7月底将基准利率上调至18%后，该国周通胀率自去年2月以来首次进入负值区域。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/russian-weekly-inflation-goes-negative-in-first-for-18-months</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 16:15:29 GMT</pubDate>
