    <item>
      <title>据称 DSV 将在 Schenker 竞标中限制裁员</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/dsv-is-said-to-offer-to-limit-layoffs-in-schenker-bidding-race</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，DSV A/S 已承诺限制德国铁路物流部门的裁员人数，此举旨在使该部门的竞购战倾向于这家丹麦公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/dsv-is-said-to-offer-to-limit-layoffs-in-schenker-bidding-race</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 16:14:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国收益率曲线反转，因疲软劳动力数据助长美联储降息预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/us-yield-curve-disinverts-as-soft-labor-data-fuels-fed-cut-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于弱于预期的劳动力市场数据增强了对美联储大幅降息的押注，美国国债收益率曲线的一个关键部分短暂转为正值。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/us-yield-curve-disinverts-as-soft-labor-data-fuels-fed-cut-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 14:32:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
